Package: onemapsgapi
Type: Package
Title: R Wrapper for OneMap.Sg's API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Jolene", "Lim", email = "jyl2187@columbia.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jolene Lim <jyl2187@columbia.edu>
Description: This package provides a suite of functions for users to easily query results from 
    the OneMap.Sg API. A function is available for every query possible in the OneMap.Sg API. 
    Using Singapore's spatial data has never been easieR!
